{"tid":2228121,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BLACKPINK 正規一輯大獲好評　YouTube 訂閱者數一天暴增 70 萬人！","createTime":"2020-10-03T10:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T16:40:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":13,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bda58b10632c41e95bc107c9ad097ce07b2aedd0","tid":2228121,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_178ab6451aa8cd288bd5d5944e92b496/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-03/130575-878157.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_178ab6451aa8cd288bd5d5944e92b496%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-03%2F130575-878157.png&h=d0cb7cc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK 昨天發行首張正規專輯〈THE ALBUM〉後立刻在全球引發熱烈迴響，經過一天後，她們也持續獲得亮眼成績！<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK 昨天（2 日）發行新專輯〈THE ALBUM〉後，主打歌 &ldquo;Lovesick Girls&rdquo; 除了立刻登上 Bugs、Genie 等韓國音源網站的即時榜首，也在美國、加拿大的 iTunes 單曲榜上奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n到了今天，&rdquo;Lovesick Girls&rdquo; 更進一步征服墨西哥、巴西、智利、西班牙、葡萄牙、希臘、波蘭、法國、瑞典、挪威⋯⋯等歐、美國家的 iTunes 單曲榜，在日本、新加坡、泰國、越南⋯⋯等亞洲國家也同樣奪冠，總共獲得 57 國的第一名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_1de457ab303c322a89210992ad39db4e/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-03/130575-878158.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_1de457ab303c322a89210992ad39db4e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-03%2F130575-878158.jpg&h=172bb311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於這次四位成員都在 MV 中展現了令人驚豔的演技，&rdquo;Lovesick Girls&rdquo; MV 公開後也再度帶動 BLACKPINK 的 YouTube 人氣，在短短一天內吸引約 70 萬名新訂閱者，目前總數也已直逼 5000 萬大關。這支掀起熱烈討論的 MV 是怎麼拍出來的呢？現在就來看看 &ldquo;Lovesick Girls&rdquo; 的幕後花絮吧！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：YG Entertainment）"},{"pid":"e167855eb1f46e687052fcee28bed2e275cc7d68","tid":2228121,"uid":16659,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-YEccr-_tQHg/X3fDXO0mbeI/AAAAAAAACwE/4JtEG_csV6UNTfqd-C1gfudr1YaIUBIFgCLcBGAsYHQ/w640-h316/1601655764